Yes.

648
00:26:54,080 --> 00:26:54,959
So,

649
00:26:54,959 --> 00:26:56,879
don't push too hard!

650
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:00,399
Fine,

651
00:27:01,159 --> 00:27:02,040
I'll give you two

