759
00:31:31,840 --> 00:31:33,560
What's going on between you two?

760
00:31:33,679 --> 00:31:34,719
Why a divorce?

761
00:31:37,199 --> 00:31:38,000
Brother-in-law,

762
00:31:38,919 --> 00:31:39,719
there's something

763
00:31:39,719 --> 00:31:41,479
