810
00:32:49,080 --> 00:32:49,879
why?

811
00:32:50,520 --> 00:32:51,840
What really happened?

812
00:32:53,520 --> 00:32:54,320
Brother-in-law,

813
00:32:55,159 --> 00:32:55,919
like I said

